data.description: Are you looking for a move-in ready home located in a more rural area but only short drives to either Harrisonville or Clinton?  Than this one is for you!  Located on a quiet street in Creighton surrounded by newer built and well maintained homes is this adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath All Electric Ranch home with an front porch ready to be decorated for the seasons!  Walking in the front door into the open space of the family room is the eye catching archways that give an open and inviting segway into the large eat-in kitchen.  The eat-in kitchen includes access to the attached garage and the first of two bathrooms, plus the backdoor to the concrete patio.  With large shade trees in the backyard this space is perfect for morning coffee or evenings outside by the BBQ pit.  The bedrooms are all located on the opposite end of the home, each with their own closets with ample space.  The main bedroom also includes its own private access to the secondary bathroom in the house, plus the main floor laundry is located in this bathroom as well.  With a newer central air unit and furnace plus a newer sump pump, all still currently under warranty, you can't go wrong with this house!  The openness of the large yard plus the short drive to either Harrisonville or Clinton put this home in a prime location, so you better act quickly before it gets swooped up by someone else!  Motivated Sellers so bring an offer!
